picture : Getty Images Amitabh Bachchan , Karan Johar and Rahul Bose are among the Bollywood stars who have mourned the loss of lives in Sikkim , which was hit by a powerful earthquake that left at least 23 people dead and 200 injured . The earthquake Sunday ( September 18 ) evening , which originated along the border of the hilly northeastern state with Nepal , has claimed at least 35 lives .